  "texts": [
    "Through the data preprocessing module, this data information is subsequently processed into the index file, the locomotive maintenance dataset, and the original dataset.",
    "Then, the text in the locomotive maintenance dataset is extracted via the locomotive customized large language model for information extraction.",
    "Next, accurate retrieval is performed in the original dataset based on the information in the index file.",
    "Finally, the indexing results and the information extraction results are merged as outputs to obtain a complete and accurate final result.",
    "Based on the comparison presented in Fig. 15, the implementation of the locomotive maintenance data standardization auxiliary tool effectively retains comprehensive information related to locomotive maintenance data."
